e\", \"types\": [\"Q47521\", \"Q4022\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seine\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seine\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the feat\", \"from\": 1006, \"to\": 1014}, {\"ngram\": \"the races\", \"from\": 1054, \"to\": 1063}, {\"ngram\": \"a 200m race\", \"from\": 1064, \"to\": 1075}, {\"ngram\": \"an obstacle course\", \"from\": 1081, \"to\": 1099}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Not even the legendary Michael Phelps, who was coached by Bob Bowman, the man now overseeing the Frenchman had done what Marchand managed.\", \"from\": 1102, \"to\": 1240, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1125, \"end\": 1139, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Michael_Phelps\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.9671667552456443e-43, \"text\": \"Michael Phelps\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10843402\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Michael_Phelps\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Michael_Phelps\"}, {\"begin\": 1160, \"end\": 1163, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bob_Bryan\", \"score\": 0.9961302026602554, \"rank\": 0.002507017874571645, \"text\": \"Bob\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10833314\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bob_Bryan\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bob_Bryan\"}, {\"begin\": 1164, \"end\": 1170, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Matt_Bowman\", \"score\": 0.999970992404629, \"rank\": 1.5022140960072043e-05, \"text\": \"Bowman\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10871364\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Matt_Bowman\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Matt_Bowman\"}, {\"begin\": 1223, \"end\": 1231, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Brad_Marchand\", \"score\": 0.9999999984147507, \"rank\": 1.0298442101059562e-09, \"text\": \"Marchand\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q11774891\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Brad_Marchand\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Brad_Marchand\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the man\", \"from\": 1172, \"to\": 1179}, {\"ngram\": \"the Frenchman\", \"from\": 1195, \"to\": 1208}]}, {\"sentence\": \"And what is more, he did it up against the most intense competition.\", \"from\": 1242, \"to\": 1310, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the most intense competition\", \"from\": 1281, \"to\": 1309}]}, {\"sentence\": \"His first race was the 200m butterfly, with Hungary's Kristof Milak, the world record holder and the Olympic champion standing in his way.\", \"from\": 1312, \"to\": 1450, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1356, \"end\": 1363, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hungary\", \"score\": 0.9125183686613445, \"rank\": 0.09581136926864012, \"text\": \"Hungary\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hungary\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hungary\"}, {\"begin\": 1374, \"end\": 1379, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Milak\", \"score\": 0.9754093777243752, \"rank\": 0.025210489465580056, \"text\": \"Milak\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Milak\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Milak\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"His first race\", \"from\": 1312, \"to\": 1326}, {\"ngram\": \"the 200m\", \"from\": 1331, \"to\": 1339}, {\"ngram\": \"butterfly\", \"from\": 1340, \"to\": 1349}, {\"ngram\": \"the world record holder\", \"from\": 1381, \"to\": 1404}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympic champion\", \"from\": 1409, \"to\": 1429}, {\"ngram\": \"his way\", \"from\": 1442, \"to\": 1449}]}, {\"sentence\": \"For 150 metres, it looked as though order would be restored.\", \"from\": 1452, \"to\": 1512, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"150 metres\", \"from\": 1456, \"to\": 1466}, {\"ngram\": \"order\", \"from\": 1488, \"to\": 1493}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Milak's personal best was a second faster than anyone in history and two better than Marchand.\", \"from\": 1513, \"to\": 1607, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1598, \"end\": 1606, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Brad_Marchand\", \"score\": 0.9999999984147507, \"rank\": 1.0298442101059562e-09, \"text\": \"Marchand\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q11774891\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Brad_Marchand\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Brad_Marchand\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"anyone\", \"from\": 1560, \"to\": 1566}, {\"ngram\": \"history\", \"from\": 1570, \"to\": 1577}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But just as the challenge looked to be too great, Marchand started his attack.\", \"from\": 1609, \"to\": 1687, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the challenge\", \"from\": 1621, \"to\": 1634}, {\"ngram\": \"Marchand\", \"from\": 1659, \"to\": 1667}, {\"ngram\": \"his attack\", \"from\": 1676, \"to\": 1686}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It is underwater where he is in a different league to anyone else, and as he managed nearly 15 metres after the final turn, lactic acid no doubt burning his arms, Marchand cut a body length deficit in half.\", \"from\": 1688, \"to\": 1894, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1851, \"end\": 1859, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Brad_Marchand\", \"score\": 0.9999999984147507, \"rank\": 1.0298442101059562e-09, \"text\": \"Marchand\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q11774891\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Brad_Marchand\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Brad_Marchand\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a different league\", \"from\": 1720, \"to\": 1738}, {\"ngram\": \"anyone\", \"from\": 1742, \"to\": 1748}, {\"ngram\": \"the final turn\", \"from\": 1796, \"to\": 1810}, {\"ngram\": \"his arms\", \"from\": 1841, \"to\": 1849}, {\"ngram\": \"a body length deficit\", \"from\": 1864, \"to\": 1885}, {\"ngram\": \"half\", \"from\": 1889, \"to\": 1893}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Suddenly it was on, and like every good predator, Marchand was relentless.\", \"from\": 1896, \"to\": 1970, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"every good predator\", \"from\": 1925, \"to\": 1944}, {\"ngram\": \"Marchand\", \"from\": 1946, \"to\": 1954}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Milak has completely dominated this event, but he had no answer to the Frenchman.\", \"from\": 1971, \"to\": 2052, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1971, \"end\": 1976, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Milak\", \"score\": 0.9754093777243752, \"rank\": 0.025210489465580056, \"text\": \"Milak\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Milak\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Milak\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"this event\", \"from\": 2002, \"to\": 2012}, {\"ngram\": \"no answer\", \"from\": 2025, \"to\": 2034}, {\"ngram\": \"the Frenchman\", \"from\": 2038, \"to\": 2051}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The crowd noise was electric.\", \"from\": 2053, \"to\": 2082, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The crowd noise\", \"from\": 2053, \"to\": 2068}]}, {\"sentence\": \"When not used for theOlympics, this arena hosts rugby and rock concerts.\", \"from\": 2083, \"to\": 2155, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"theOlympics\", \"from\": 2101, \"to\": 2112}, {\"ngram\": \"this arena\", \"from\": 2114, \"to\": 2124}, {\"ngram\": \"rugby and rock concerts\", \"from\": 2131, \"to\": 2154}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It may never have experienced a crescendo like this though.\", \"from\": 2156, \"to\": 2215, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a crescendo\", \"from\": 2186, \"to\": 2197}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He touched home in a time of 1:51.21, breaking Milak's Olympic record and overtaking Phelps as the second fastest man ever in the event.\", \"from\": 2217, \"to\": 2353, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2264, \"end\": 2269, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Milak\", \"score\": 0.9754093777243752, \"rank\": 0.025210489465580056, \"text\": \"Milak\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Milak\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Milak\"}, {\"begin\": 2302, \"end\": 2308, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/William_H._Phelps_Sr.\", \"score\": 0.9999989388958229, \"rank\": 1.0610887639375669e-06, \"text\": \"Phelps\", \"types\": [\"Q901\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/William_H._Phelps_Sr.\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/William_H._Phelps_Sr.\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a time\", \"from\": 2236, \"to\": 2242}, {\"ngram\": \"1:51.21\", \"from\": 2246, \"to\": 2253}, {\"ngram\": \"the second fastest man\", \"from\": 2312, \"to\": 2334}, {\"ngram\": \"the event\", \"from\": 2343, \"to\": 2352}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Having done the unthinkable, Marchand then had to rest and recover.\", \"from\": 2355, \"to\": 2422, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Marchand\", \"from\": 2384, \"to\": 2392}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Two hours in swimming is nothing, and even less so when you have a victory ceremony and a first Marseillaise to sing.\", \"from\": 2423, \"to\": 2540, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Two hours\", \"from\": 2423, \"to\": 2432}, {\"ngram\": \"swimming\", \"from\": 2436, \"to\": 2444}, {\"ngram\": \"nothing\", \"from\": 2448, \"to\": 2455}, {\"ngram\": \"a victory ceremony\", \"from\": 2488, \"to\": 2506}, {\"ngram\": \"a first Marseillaise\", \"from\": 2511, \"to\": 2531}]}, {\"sentence\": \"With that behind him, he returned for his second challenge of the night - 200m breaststroke.\", \"from\": 2542, \"to\": 2634, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"his second challenge\", \"from\": 2580, \"to\": 2600}, {\"ngram\": \"the night\", \"from\": 2604, \"to\": 2613}, {\"ngram\": \"200m breaststroke\", \"from\": 2616, \"to\": 2633}]}, {\"sentence\": \"This time, it was Olympic champion and former world record holder Zac Stubblety-Cook who was his main rival.\", \"from\": 2636, \"to\": 2744, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2702, \"end\": 2720, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Zac_Stubblety-Cook\", \"score\": 0.9999995230460855, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Zac Stubblety-Cook\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10843402\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Zac_Stubblety-Cook\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Zac_Stubblety-Cook\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Olympic champion\", \"from\": 2654, \"to\": 2670}, {\"ngram\": \"his main rival\", \"from\": 2729, \"to\": 2743}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The Australian is renowned for his finishing speed, often making up huge deficits to triumph.\", \"from\": 2746, \"to\": 2839, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2746, \"end\": 2760, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/The_Australian\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.1713014883712764e-14, \"text\": \"The Australian\", \"types\": [\"Q386724\", \"Q234460\", \"Q11032\", \"Q1092563\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/The_Australian\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/The_Australian\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"his finishing speed\", \"from\": 2777, \"to\": 2796}, {\"ngram\": \"huge deficits\", \"from\": 2814, \"to\": 2827}]}, {\"sentence\": \"When Marchand went out under world record pace, the fear was that the fatigue would catch up with him.\", \"from\": 2840, \"to\": 2942, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Marchand\", \"from\": 2845, \"to\": 2853}, {\"ngram\": \"world record pace\", \"from\": 2869, \"to\": 2886}, {\"ngram\": \"the fear\", \"from\": 2888, \"to\": 2896}, {\"ngram\": \"the fatigue\", \"from\": 2906, \"to\": 2917}]}, {\"sentence\": \"As he tired, surely then Stubblety-Cook could strike.\", \"from\": 2944, \"to\": 2997, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Stubblety-Cook\", \"from\": 2969, \"to\": 2983}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But Marchand is no mere human.\", \"from\": 2999, \"to\": 3029, \"entities\": [{\"begi